<pre>|Name         |Blueberry2Theme|
|Description  |A ~TiddlyWiki Blueberry-colors theme|
|Version      |1.0.1|
|Author       |? (Various ideas were shamesslessly taken from and suggested by Simon Baird, Clint Checketts and Christine Hodges); Yakov Litvin (adoption to TW 2.10.1, various updates, packing into an actual theme)|
